These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, jazz, funk, trance
1. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of trance##1
2. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of funk##1
3. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | funk | jazz | metal | trance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, chinchilla, rat, goat
1. the owner of the goat is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | fish | rat | chinchilla | goat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, collecting, dancing
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | collecting | cooking | drawing | dancing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, taxi, skateboard
1. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Transport   | taxi | helicopter | motorbike | skateboard |

